list.abstract: 含义过夜，多指在外暂住。

yingyinNormal.en: Looking at the snapshots greg has taken over time, what strikes me is not just the roads themselves, but the number of housing developments hugging the highways.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看看这些快照，格林已经很好的掌握了时间，让我震撼的不仅仅是道路，还有在高速公路附近出现的越来越多的房屋。

yingyinNormal.en: What is that? That's America's housing market.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么事？倒塌的正是美国房地产市场。

yingyinNormal.en: No, no, no, no. No stocks. I want to short the housing market.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，不是股票，我想要做空房地产市场。

yingyinNormal.en: No, no. This is putting up sheetrock at a housing project in Rosemead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，是给罗斯密市的一间住宅安装石膏板。

yingyinNormal.en: No. That can't be right. There were $500 billion in housing bonds sold last year alone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不可能，单单去年就有五千亿的房地产债券售出。

yingyinNormal.en: He decided to spend his summer, building sustainable housing for the poor. Guess where, Sokovia.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他想利用暑假给穷人建生态住宅，猜猜是哪？索科威亚。

yingyinNormal.en: It's important to understand because it's what allowed a housing crisis to become a nationwide economic disaster.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是很重要的概念，因为它会让房地产危机成为全国金融危机。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, I don't think that they even know what they've made. The housing market is propped up on these bad loans, and I'm...
yingyinNormal.zh: 听着，我觉得他们都不知道自己创造了什么，房地产市场是由这些糟糕的房贷撑起来的。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. Two years ago, Bennie Cleager in Morgan's bond department also started shorting subprime housing, $2 billion in BBBs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，两年前 本尼·克里格在摩根的债券部门也在做空次级房贷，二十亿做空3B级公司。

yingyinNormal.en: Really? But the housing market is rock solid. Greenspan just said bubbles are regional, defaults are rare. Tell them I'll be there in a minute.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是吗？房地产市场可是稳如磐石啊，格林斯潘刚刚才说泡沫是区域性的，违约是少见的，告诉他们我一会儿就来。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Singapore has seen a big inflow of foreigners, which has mainly pushed up the price of <highlight>housing</highlight> and other living costs.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大量外国人涌入新加坡，这主要推高了房价和其他生活成本。

examination_example.sentence: With a limited <highlight>housing</highlight> supply, the average house prices have risen sharply by over 93 percent between 2010 and 2014.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 由于住房供应有限，2010年至2014年间，平均房价大幅上涨了93%以上。
